  "YangsThoughts": "The Banshee IIC is a Clan second-line variant of a Star League-era design, pressed back into service due to shortages. The original Banshee, while iconic, had notable flaws. As OmniMechs advanced, older chassis like the Banshee IIC were relegated to garrisons or caches. The Star Adders kept the largest stockpiles. Over time, it was upgraded from SLDF weaponry standards. Recent IIC and IIC 2 variants improve on the Defiance BNC-5S design using advanced Clan technology, making the Banshee a more capable and dangerous battlefield machine..",
